summary: Runtime and measured boot policy management via MCP server
description: |
    Tests policy CRUD operations through MCP tools:
    import, list, get, update, and delete for both
    runtime policies and measured boot policies.
contact: Marek Safarik <msafarik@redhat.com>
component:
  - keylime-mcp
framework: shell
test: cd ${TMT_TREE} && go test -v -count=1 -timeout=300s -tags=functional ./functional-tests/policy-management/
require:
  - golang
  - keylime
duration: 5m
enabled: true
